snippet.title: Coreborn: Nations of the Ultracore - Early Access Trailer
snippet.description:
Coreborn: Nations of the Ultracore is a social survival sandbox game that invites players to venture to the world of Tormentosia, a land torn apart by the evil Sorgoth and his powerful armies. Join fellow adventurers online, build and defend your home, and reclaim the land from the evil forces of Sorgoth!

Coreborn: Nations of the Ultracore will be launching into Early Access on PC on July 18th. Players can wishlist Coreborn on Steam right now!

WISHLIST NOW on Steam:  https://bit.ly/WishlistCoreborn
Join the Coreborn Discord for updates and playtests:  https://discord.gg/coreborn
Follow on Twitter:  https://twitter.com/playcoreborn?s=21&t=-GzgCEicwpEURyfc3Par-g
Follow on TikTok:  https://www.tiktok.com/@playcoreborn?_t=8cMsXLxY0SY&_r=1
